minimem (0.9.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Scanner CPU budget system (scanner_cpu_budget_ms, scanner_mark_budget_pages)
  * Cursor-based resumption for mark and sweep phases
  * MMU notifier for process exit cleanup on stock kernels
  * Kretprobe fault handler enabling scanner sweep on unpatched kernels
  * Per-process compression via compress_pid sysfs attribute
  * scanner_mark_yielded and scanner_sweep_yielded stats
  * Fix scanner_cycles_empty being incremented on every cycle

